2008-10-09    <ensmjc@enpc-adm34.bath.ac.uk>

	* src/mpole.c moved fundamental multipole functions (inverse
	distances, moment computations, etc.) into a separate file to make
	re-use in other libraries easier.

	Copyright (C) 2006, 2007, 2008 by Michael Carley

	2008-10-06    <ensmjc@enpc-adm34.bath.ac.uk>

	* src/curl.c (calc_curl): Added direct integration for in-box
	calculations on curl fields. This still needs user-selectable
	parameters for quadrature selection (or, better, a good
	tolerance-based method).
	
2008-10-03    <ensmjc@enpc-adm34.bath.ac.uk>

	* src/multipole.c (gtv_multipole_field_amm): Added support for
	curl fields.

2008-08-20    <ensmjc@enpc-adm34.bath.ac.uk>

	* src/tetrahedron.c (gtv_tetrahedron_radius_ratio): added to
	calculate radius ratio quality measure for a tetrahedron.

	* tools/gtv-check.c (main): now calls gtv_volume_print_stats for
	full geometric statistics information.

	* src/volume.c (gtv_volume_quality_stats): Added function to fill
	GtvVolumeQualityStats struct.

	* src/gtv.h ("C"): Added GtvVolumeQualityStats struct.

	* src/tetrahedron.c (gtv_tetrahedron_radius_ratio): Added quality
	measure for tetrahedra.

2008-07-29    <ensmjc@enpc-adm34.bath.ac.uk>

	* src/multipole.c: Added functions to generate multipole moments
	for volumes

	* src/octtree.c: Added functions to generate octtrees for volumes.
	
2008-04-23    <ensmjc@enpc-adm34.bath.ac.uk>

	* src/volume.c: Added functions to write GMSH format 2.0 files and
	to read gmsh legacy formats.

2008-03-18    <ensmjc@enpc-adm34.bath.ac.uk>

	* src/facet.c: Added gtv_vertex_is_boundary()

2008-03-10    <ensmjc@enpc-adm34.bath.ac.uk>

	* src/volume.c: added functions to read GMSH format 2.0 msh files.

