2007-02-18    <michael@rpc-ensmjc.icam.fr>

	* src/tetrahedron.c: Rewrote tetrahedron_destroy

	* src/volume.c: Added gtv_volume_write.
	Added gtv_volume_read

	* src/parents.c (gtv_edge_facet_number): Function to find number
	of GtvFacets using an edge.
	(gtv_facet_cell_number): Function to find number of GtvCells using
	a facet. 

	* src/facet.c (gtv_facet_new): Corrected to set triangle lists of
	edges properly.

	* src/volume.c: Added gtv_volume_foreach_cell/facet/edge/vertex. 

	* src/tetrahedron.c: Added gtv_tetrahedron_apex to find vertex of
	a tetrahedron which does not lie on the first facet.
	Added gtv_tetrahedron_vertices to find vertices of a tetrahedron.


